
Dependencies:

 * Qt >= 4.7
 * Qt Mobility >= 1.1 Declarative Plugins
 * Qt Declarative Particles Plugin (libqt4-declarative-particles)

Creating a new release:

 1.) Hack, hack, hack
 2.) Update version in src/config.h
 3.) Run "make release" (to update specfiles, etc..)
 4.) Commit everything, tag using "git tag 1.0.x"
 5.) Push stuff: git push ; git push --tags
 6.) Run "make release" again
 7.) Upload mong.spec + the source tarball to the OBS

